## Phase 4: CLI Tool Development

### 4.1 CLI Architecture
CLI implemented in `packages/cli` with commands:
- `add`: Add components to your project
- `init`: Initialize configuration

Component templates for Button, Input, Field, Alert Dialog, Accordion, Context Menu, and Tabs are available in `packages/cli/templates/`.

### 4.2 Component Registry
Registry system in `packages/cli/src/utils/registry.ts` tracks available components and their files/dependencies. Fully tested with real user installation scenarios.

